<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探不见了，” 罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得去一下警察总局。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她对朋友们喊道：“别等我，我......嗯......掉东西了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察总局的停车场空荡荡的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警车都去哪里了？” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人又都去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当罗西进去后，她惊讶地睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙是歪的，地板是斜的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里发生什么事了？” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么像游乐园里的趣味屋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走廊一边挂满了镜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一面镜子让罗西看起来又高又瘦，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外一面镜子让她的头显得特别大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西进了休息室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咖啡机开着，饼干放在柜子上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>广播里播放着音乐，就是一个人也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挠了挠头。“真奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！扑通！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西脚下的地板开始倾斜，她滑进了黑暗中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西落在地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是火箭女孩儿吗？” 史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>通过夜光视力，罗西发现自己在一个水泥房里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侦探站在罗西的旁边，别的警官也都在这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咧嘴笑了。“你们是在玩儿捉迷藏吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探看上去很恼火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，现在不是开玩笑的时候。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们从昨天起就被困在这里了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！对不起！这栋楼里发生了什么事？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怎么看上去像一个趣味屋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们雇了一个建筑工人修理这栋大楼，” 史密斯侦探叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很明显他做得太差了。我们现在连大楼都不能用了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“建筑工人是谁？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克·哈默，” 史密斯侦探说，“我们再也不会雇他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位警官走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么从这里出去呢？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西哈哈大笑。“这个很容易。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞起来把警官们带到了休息室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探拿起一块饼干，咬了一口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女警官看到电话机的灯在闪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 她说，“我们有留言。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她按了第一条留言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？我很担心我的朋友布兰达和丹·杜雷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨天他们搬了新家，在十水坑街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我打了电话，也敲了门，但都没人应。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他打电话的人也留了类似的留言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些人还打了好几次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探咽下最后一口饼干。“天啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>